===============
  File Format  
===============

Sound quality is from the original recording perp, so there's
 a bit of radio crackling, the occasional MSN login. That said
 you'll be hard pushed to find this set ANYWHERE, and they're
 great if you're not an audio-nazi!
I've ID3 tagged them (V2.something) using Kid3, properly, so
 they'll sit nicely in your MP3 player for your journey to
 work!

==========================
  Here man, that's mint!  
==========================

Particular favourites are:
  The Count Of Monte Cristo
  Cleopatra
  Fall Of The House Of Usher

=============
  Nota Bene  
=============

I don't know all the Narrators, but a few of them are there, if
 anyone can comment with updates on THEPIRATEBAY only, it'd be
 rather nice!
Also, categorized under Music rather than Audio book, the reason
 is that the project was to help educate the 'yoof' about modern-
 classical literature. GET EDJOOKATED NOW!
